{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 15,
  "title": "第十五章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "古之善為士者，微妙玄通，深不可識。夫唯不可識，故強為之容。豫焉若冬涉川，"
    },
    {
      "text": "猶兮若畏四鄰，"
    },
    {
      "text": "儼兮其若容，渙兮若冰之將釋，敦兮其若樸，曠兮其若谷，混兮其若濁。"
    },
    {
      "text": "孰能濁以靜之徐清？孰能安以久動之徐生？"
    },
    {
      "text": "保此道者不欲盈，"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯不盈，故能蔽不新成。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 36
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "冬之涉川，豫然若欲度、若不欲度，其情不可得見之貌也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "四鄰合攻中央之主，猶然不知所趣向者也。上德之人，其端兆不可覩，德趣不可見，亦猶此也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 32
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "凡此諸若，皆言其容象不可得而形名也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫晦以理物則得明，濁以靜物則得清，安以動物則得生，此自然之道也。孰能者，言其難也。徐者，詳慎也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "盈必溢也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "蔽，覆蓋也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
